Instructions for testing application 

1.) Open up DVD 

2.) Click the folder marked “BHS” which contains the application

3.) Click “BHS.xcodeprog” file which will open up the file in the Xcode IDE

4.) From there just click “⌘ + R” or the run button  

-The app will then load followed by a brief overview of the applications contents, which contains banner images

-Activities are sorted by date, and one can add an activity with the Activities name, date, location, time, contact, and even a picture 

-One click an activity to go over its contents again, as well click the activities location to find it on the built in maps

-There is also a images button in the tool bar which displays a scrolling banner image of activity pictures
